OL,3,CGovernment must 'revise' plan for Post
OL,4,COffice compensation, MPs say
OL,6,FThe government must "revise" it's
OL,7,Fcompensation plan for victims of the
OL,8,FPost Office scandal, MPs demand.
OL,10,FIn an unusual intervention, members of
OL,11,Fthe Business and Trade Committee have
OL,12,Furged the government to go further in
OL,13,Fits plan to deliver justice for
OL,14,Fvictims of the scandal, saying the
OL,15,Fcurrent response "fell short of what
OL,16,Fis needed".
OL,18,FMore than 4,000 victims of the Horizon
OL,19,Fscandal are still waiting to settle
OL,20,Ftheir claims, with many dying before
OL,21,Freceiving their compensation.
