OL,3,CGovernment must 'revise' plan for Post
OL,4,COffice compensation, MPs say
OL,6,FRecommendations the MPs are urging the
OL,7,Fgovernment to reconsider include -
OL,8,Fgiving some claimants upfront legal
OL,9,Fadvice at the start of their claim,
OL,10,Fcreating binding timeframes for
OL,11,Fhanding out compensation, and bringing
OL,12,Fall compensation management into the
OL,13,Fcontrol of the Department for Business
OL,14,Fand Trade (DBT).
OL,16,FEarlier this month the government
OL,17,Fannounced responsibility for managing
OL,18,Fmost compensation claims will be
OL,19,Ftransferred from the Post Office to
OL,20,Fthe DBT.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
