OL,3,CGovernment must 'revise' plan for Post
OL,4,COffice compensation, MPs say
OL,6,FBut the committee says it's a
OL,7,F"mistake" to not also transfer claims
OL,8,Funder the Horizon Shortfall Scheme to
OL,9,FDBT, which the Post Office itself has
OL,10,Fadvised ministers should do.
OL,12,FMore than 900 sub-postmasters were
OL,13,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,14,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,15,F2000 and 2015, as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,16,FHorizon system made it seem money had
OL,17,Fgone missing at their branches. The
OL,18,Fscandal has since been considered one
OL,19,Fof Britain's most widespread
OL,20,Fmiscarriages of justice in history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
