OL,3,CGovernment must 'revise' plan for Post
OL,4,COffice compensation, MPs say
OL,6,FChair of the Committee Liam Byrne
OL,7,Fsaid: "The new government has made
OL,8,Fextremely important progress in
OL,9,Faccelerating redress payment to the
OL,10,Fvictims of the biggest miscarriage of
OL,11,Fjustice in British legal history.
OL,13,F"But too many are still waiting too
OL,14,Flong, and former sub-postmasters are
OL,15,Fstill dying before they receive
OL,16,Fjustice. That is wrong.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
